list.description:
After I finished the previous tutorial loop and before I got to this one, I saw the following series of error messages:

Agave Recovery Wizard

The Agave Recovery Wizard is attempting to recover Echo.exe. 
Do not turn off your computer.

[XXXXX->							]


The progress bar gets to about 25% and then another dialog appears. 


⛔ Recovery failed. 

Error 713: File(s) missing or corrupt. 

Agave will attempt to continue startup. Do not turn off your computer. 

						OK


Loading screen returns followed by the same Agave Recovery Wizard window. 

⚠️

 Startup cannot continue because of a problem at: 

C:\Users\Dad\Documents\Work\Asphodel\Echo.exe

Click OK to open the Agave Recovery Wizard.
